newplayerpack.name: New Player Pack
newplayerpack.description: A pack to get you started with Dank Memer.

prestigepack.name: Prestige Pack
prestigepack.description: A pack to get you back on your feet after prestiging.

antirobpack.name: Anti-Rob Pack
antirobpack.description: A pack containing basic items to not get robbed.

grindpack.name: Grind Pack
grindpack.description: A pack containing items to start your adventure with grinding.

patreonpack.name: Patreon Pack
patreonpack.description: A pack you get once per week for being a patron!

phone.name: Cell Phone
phone.description: Text your friends! Fun for the entire family
phone.longdescription: Use your cell phone to text your friends via the notifications system, or ring the police in the case of an emergency or robbery. Your phone won't be removed on use, however mis-using it (such as dialing police when there's no emergency) may cost you money.

padlock.name: Padlock
padlock.description: Lock a padlock on your wallet to prevent people from robbing you
padlock.longdescription: Lock a padlock on your wallet to prevent people from robbing you. This is a one-time use item; once the lock is broken or removed, it won't come back or do anything unless you buy another one. It will not ALWAYS break, but it has a chance to break when someone tries to steal from you.

laptop.name: Laptop
laptop.longdescription: A collectible item that used to allow you access the postmemes command. A relic of the past.

sand.name: Box of Sand
sand.description: Chuck some sand in someone's face to prevent them from robbing you
sand.longdescription: Throw a box of sand in someone's eyes to prevent them from robbing anyone for 30 minutes.
sand.effects: There's a chance the sand will blow back into your face, and you won't be able to steal from the person you mentioned.

apple.name: Apple
apple.description: An apple a day keeps the what away? Avoid item loss on death!
apple.longdescription: Eating this once a day makes it so you do not lose any inventory items or active items if you die. The lifesaver takes priority over this effect. (Lasts 24 hours)

landmine.name: Landmine
landmine.description: Blows up when someone steps on it when trying to steal from you, potentially killing them
landmine.longdescription: If someone tries to steal from you there's a 50% chance they will die from blowing up. Lasts 24 hours.

fakeid.name: Fake ID
fakeid.description: Disguise your identity from robbers using a wishlist!

alcohol.name: Alcohol
alcohol.description: Down some alcohol and maybe you'll get lucky! Maybe.
alcohol.longdescription: Drink a bottle of alcohol, and have the potential to gain a small luck boost that will grant you better luck in stealing from others. However, you become more susceptible to being stolen from!
alcohol.effects: There's a 10% chance you'll die from alcohol poisoning (meaning you'll lose all of your coins). You're also more prone to losing coins and being stolen from.

shovel.name: Shovel
shovel.longdescription: This shovel allows you to use the dig command, which can give you lots of different types of items!

fishingpole.name: Fishing Pole
fishingpole.longdescription: This fishing pole allows you to use the fish command, which can give you lots of different types of items!

huntingrifle.name: Hunting Rifle
huntingrifle.longdescription: This hunting rifle allows you to use the hunt command, which can give you lots of different types of items!

coinbomb.name: Coin Bomb
coinbomb.description: A bomb that explodes coins for other people to pick up
coinbomb.longdescription: A bomb that explodes coins for other people to pick up. Dispenses anywhere from ⏣ 2,000 - ⏣ 15,000 for other people on the server to pick up in chat. Basically used to get people active in chat and share some coins!

horseshoe.name: Lucky Horseshoe
horseshoe.description: Using this increases your luck in some commands for 15 minutes!
horseshoe.longdescription: No one is sure exactly how much this increased your luck by, but it's different for each command! This affects hunt, fish, beg, search, crime, postmemes, steal, dig, and gamble!

spinner.name: Fidget Spinner
spinner.description: Gain a temporary multiplier depending on how long you can spin your fidget spinner!
spinner.longdescription: Spin your fidget spinner, and gain anywhere from a **5% to a 40%** multiplier boost for 10 minutes depending on how long your fidget spinner spins for.

lifesaver.name: Life Saver
lifesaver.description: Quite literally saves your life and keeps you from dying!
lifesaver.longdescription: Having one in your inventory prevents death and uses one when you almost die. This is used BEFORE the apple's effects.

tidepod.name: Tidepod
tidepod.description: Risking your life for a multiplier? Sounds great!
tidepod.longdescription: Eat a Tidepod, risking your life to have the potential to gain a **50%** multiplier for **2 whole hours**.
tidepod.effects: There's a high chance you'll injure yourself from the tidepod and die (meaning you lose all coins).

wishlist.name: Robbers Wishlist
wishlist.description: A robber's best friend! List all robbable users in a server!
wishlist.longdescription: This item when used gives a list of users that aren't passive and do not have a fake ID on. Basically, anyone who is robbable :D

pepe.name: Rare Pepe
pepe.description: A lone rare pepe, made to collect and flex how many you can get compared to your friends.
pepe.longdescription: The rare pepe is only used for collecting or flexing on normies who cannot afford one. Although basically anyone can afford one these days...

cheese.name: Shredded Cheese
cheese.description: A mystic bag of light-golden shredded cheese. Earn an XP multiplier!
cheese.longdescription: Dump an entire bag of shredded cheese into your face hole. For every bag of shredded cheese consumed, you get a stacking EXP multiplier, capping at **85%** (**30** bags of cheese consumed).
cheese.effects: There's a small chance your lactose intolerance acts up and you lose some experience points.

pizza.name: Pizza Slice
pizza.description: Eat this for a chunky xp multiplier!
pizza.longdescription: Eating this perfect pizza slice will give you +250% xp gains for an hour.

ring.name: Engagement Ring
ring.longdescription:
Propose to someone!
Marriage has a lot of benefits and downsides, be careful!

pepecoin.name: Pepe Coin
pepecoin.description: A pretty rare coin, probably only fairly rich people have this!
pepecoin.longdescription: This coin is primarily for flexing on normies who cannot afford one. Once upon a time it was the most expensive item on the bot!

pepemedal.name: Pepe Medal
pepemedal.description: A medal only the top 5% of players have!
pepemedal.longdescription: Owning this medal gives you an extra 5% steal shields (does not stack). Otherwise, it is used to flex on normies who cannot afford one!

pepetrophy.name: Pepe Trophy
pepetrophy.description: A trophy to flex how rich you are! You are rich enough to afford this... right?
pepetrophy.longdescription: Having this trophy gives you a 5% multiplier, an extra 10% steal shields, and an extra 5% chance at random events spawning (does not stack). Otherwise, it is used to flex on normies who cannot afford one!

pepecrown.name: Pepe Crown
pepecrown.description: Literally only the richest of the richest of the richest of the richest of the richest of the rich will hold these beloved crowns. At least until another expensive item comes along LOL.
pepecrown.longdescription: Having this crown raises the max wallet to gamble to 100 million. This does not stack. This item doesn't have as much function as some other collectables, but has double the style.

fartinabottle.name: Fart In A Bottle
fartinabottle.description: A really stinky bottle. Should you sniff it? "You're either a smart fella, or a fart smella." -TheLazyTownie

sugarskull.name: Sugar Skull
sugarskull.description: Día de los Muertos 2021 limited time item

pepesus.name: Pepe Sus
pepesus.description: Pepe is looking a little SUS today

toiletpaper.name: Toilet Paper
toiletpaper.description: If we learned anything during the pandemic, it's that TP is VALUABLE

stocking.name: Holiday Stocking
stocking.description: A holiday 2021 limited time item from drop sales only

enchantedbad.name: Enchanted Badosz's Card
enchantedbad.description: Perfectly balanced, as all things should be. Change your pet to any other type and keep their stats, consumed on use.

cursedpepe.name: Cursed Pepe
cursedpepe.description: A pepe that NOT EVEN a mother could love.

boxedchocolates.name: Boxed Chocolates
boxedchocolates.description: A boxy box of boxed chocolates to give to your partner to prove your love! (Level up your marriage by 3 weeks upon eating)

scepter.name: Royal Scepter
scepter.description: A royal scepter such as this is worth close to 50k gold carats, dang! You can either use this item to obtain royalty embedded colours or keep it in your collection.

letter.name: The Letter
letter.description: A custom item containing a message from ANANT#5998, NotARSenic#0709 and Dauntless#0711. What's that message? Open it up to find out!

camera.name: Camera
camera.description: A streamer item that helps you with amount of viewers.

microphone.name: Microphone
microphone.description: A streamer item that helps you with stability of your stream.

soundcard.name: Sound Card
soundcard.description: A meta streamer item that helps you get other streamer items.

ringlight.name: Ring Light
ringlight.description: A streamer item that lowers your min time between stream interactions.

greenscreen.name: Green Screen
greenscreen.description: A streamer item that increases your revenue.

headphones.name: Headphones
headphones.description: A streamer item that increases your max idle time.

creditcard.name: Credit Card
creditcard.description: Use this credit card to buy a friend some premium perks!
creditcard.longdescription: You can use this card to "buy" someone 5 days of premium perks for Dank Memer. (The $2 perk value)

streakfreeze.name: Streak Freeze
streakfreeze.description: This item will prevent you from losing your daily streak ONE time.
streakfreeze.longdescription: Using this item will turn it into an active item that lasts 30 days. After it's active, if you run daily after missing 1+ days you will retain your streak. This is automatically destroyed at that point.

ducttape.name: Duct Tape
ducttape.description: Use this tape to craft certain items with the craft command!
ducttape.longdescription: This item is purely used in the craft command to bond items together!

prestigecoin.name: Prestige Coin
prestigecoin.description: Earned from prestiging, use this coin to activate your post-prestige bonus multi. It gives you 6 hours worth of 350% multiplier.

aetheryxflower.name: Aetheryx' Flower
aetheryxflower.description: A no longer vibrant red flower, a wisp of it's former self.

karen.name: Literally Karen
karen.description: The karens on this bot are really annoying. You know who they are.

melmsiebeard.name: Melmsie's Beard
melmsiebeard.description: Who shaved this off their face, that seems gross.

beanmp3.name: Bean Mp3 Player
beanmp3.description: The long lost voice of a bean. This item can only be used once before it explodes from too much B E A N.

badoszcard.name: Badosz's Card
badoszcard.description: A real king in the sleeve.

bunnysapron.name: Bunny's Apron
bunnysapron.description: A handmade pink apron with bunny ears stitched to the pocket, finely crafted for Michelin Star chefs, it is mainly found in the Kitchen.

bluesplane.name: Blue's Plane
bluesplane.description: This top of-the-line aircraft carries only the most prestigious of passengers

yengpaw.name: Yeng Gang
yengpaw.description: A squishy paw that can relieve stress and make you smile. SQUISH! SQUISH! SQUISH!

lotterywinner.name: Winning Lottery Ticket
lotterywinner.description: Proof that you won the lottery once upon a time
lotterywinner.longdescription: This allows you to brag to your friends or enemies about winning the lottery, and also gives you a 2% higher chance at random events. The ultimate flex.

cutters.name: Bolt Cutters
cutters.description: This will bypass any padlocks while robbing.
cutters.longdescription: Originally for developers only, this item instantly breaks all padlocks.

reversal.name: Reversal Card
reversal.description: A legacy item from a simpler time in Dank Memer. This item is now just a collectable for those who already had them in the past.
reversal.longdescription: Reversal cards used to reverse a steal that someone performed on you. Due to being SUPER buggy and causing multiple exploits, they were removed. They are now back for those who already had them in their inventories, but not functional and just for collecting.

eye.name: Odd Eye
eye.description: This eye is odd, and fairly creepy. It has probably close to 20k veins, ew.

chillpill.name: Chill Pill
chillpill.description: Just take a chill pill and relax, sheesh

banknote.name: Bank Note
banknote.description: Use this to expand your bank space!
banknote.longdescription: You can either use this note to expand your bank space by 10000-100000 or sell it for some coins. Your choice really. Expanded bank space does not reset on prestige (regular bank space earned via running commands does)

pinkphallicobject.name: Pink Phallic Object
pinkphallicobject.description: Swear on me mum's life it's not a dildo. Send it to a friend!
pinkphallicobject.longdescription: Send people the gift of pink phallic shaped items. Using this will send it to the person of your choice's inventory for them to find later.

bluephallicobject.name: Blue Phallic Object
bluephallicobject.description: A blue twist on a pink favorite!
bluephallicobject.longdescription: This is simply a collectable, and NOT for any type of use. ANY type of use guys, please.

purplephallicobject.name: Purple Phallic Object
purplephallicobject.description: A purple twist on a pink favorite!
purplephallicobject.longdescription: This is simply a collectable, and NOT for any type of use. ANY type of use guys, please.

orangephallicobject.name: Orange Phallic Object
orangephallicobject.description: An orange twist on a pink favorite!
orangephallicobject.longdescription: This is simply a collectable, and NOT for any type of use. ANY type of use guys, please.

goldenphallicobject.name: Golden Phallic Object
goldenphallicobject.description: A golden twist on a pink favorite!
goldenphallicobject.longdescription: This is simply a collectable, and NOT for any type of use. ANY type of use guys, please.

multiphallicobject.name: Multi Colored Phallic Object
multiphallicobject.description: A colorful twist on a pink favorite!
multiphallicobject.longdescription: This is simply a collectable, and NOT for any type of use. ANY type of use guys, please.

pepestatue.name: Pepe Statue
pepestatue.description: A neat collectable statue, looks very similar to a coin you can buy.

snowflake.name: Snowflake
snowflake.description: Every snowflake is unique... but not in this bot

tree.name: Literally a Tree
tree.description: This is just a plain tree

christmastree.name: Christmas Tree
christmastree.description: A beautiful Christmas tree, purely for collecting

berriesandcream.name: Berries and Cream
berriesandcream.description: I'm a little lad who loves...
berriesandcream.longdescription: A limited time item from a random event, use this item to send it to someone who loves berries and cream!

fool.name: Fool's Notif
fool.description: Fool a friend with this item, give them a random fake notification!
fool.longdescription: Using this on a user will give them a fake notification that is ALMOST real, but can be told apart from the real thing if they look close enough...

snowball.name: Snowball
snowball.description: Chuck a snowball at someone and stun them!
snowball.longdescription: Throw a snowball at someone else and prevent them from doing anything bad to you for a few minutes like robbing you, or putting negative items on you!

santashat.name: Santa's Hat
santashat.description: Put on Santa's hat and join in on the holiday spirit!
santashat.longdescription: Equip Santa's hat and turn all embed colors (the color on the side of embeds) into Christmas themed colors!

gift.name: Friend's Gift
gift.description: Buy this to send to a friend to open
gift.longdescription: This item is not able to be opened, only sent. Once you use it with `pls use friend`, the person who receives it will be able to open a Gift Box (Holiday lootbox).

jacky.name: Jacky o' Lanty
jacky.description: Put on a Jacky and join in on the spooky season!
jacky.longdescription: Equip this and turn all embed colors (the color on the side of embeds) into spooky season colors.

candy.name: Candy
candy.longdescription: Consuming this candy will give you a random amount of coins. Yum!

blob.name: Blob
blob.description: This is just a shell of it's former self, earned for doing basically absolutely nothing during the blob event

cupidsbigtoe.name: Cupid's Big Toe
cupidsbigtoe.description: Enhance your multiplier with Cupid's presence!
cupidsbigtoe.longdescription: Applies a multiplier of **69%** for **69 seconds**. Limited time item for valentines day!

meteorite.name: Meteorite
meteorite.description: A chunk of space rock with some interesting signs of life on it

jarofsingularity.name: Jar Of Singularity
jarofsingularity.description: This could be important in the future...

blackhole.name: Black Hole
blackhole.description: This item eats some gained items.
blackhole.longdescription: This item is a shady little lottery. When you have one in your inventory, you have a random chance to have a gained item (from commands ran, not from your inv) to be sucked into the black hole and put into an item lottery. This also enters you to win said item lottery and get a share of ALL the items entered.

aliensample.name: Alien Sample
aliensample.description: A collectible sample of alien tissue

adventureticket.name: Adventure Ticket
adventureticket.description: A ticket to start an adventure!
adventureticket.longdescription: Can be found in limited stock in the shop, from voting, or from being a patron! These are used to start an adventure in the adventure command.

empoweredfartbottle.name: Empowered Fart Bottle
empoweredfartbottle.description: A really POWERFULLY stinky bottle. You should NOT sniff it! (The same as a fart bottle but you cannot fail)

starfragment.name: Star Fragment
starfragment.description: A fragment of a shooting star. I wonder what this can be used for?

shootingstar.name: Shooting Star
shootingstar.description: Make a wish! Or don't, I can't force you.

giftbox.name: Gift Box
giftbox.description: A gift from a good friend

daily.name: Daily Box
daily.description: A reward for voting for Dank Memer! Using this box also gives you a 10 minute double xp boost.

bundlebox.name: Bundle Box
bundlebox.description: This has a 50% chance for 1 bread and 50% chance for an empowered fart bottle. If you get bread and are unhappy with this outcome, please email badosz@dankmemer.gg for a personal apology as this was his idea. If his personal apology is not to your liking, please let us know. (No refunds though)

normie.name: Normie Box
normie.description: Can't get more basic than this

dank.name: Dank Box
dank.description: Dank rewards for a dank user

god.name: God Box
god.description: What the hell this is op god tier box.

patreon.name: Patreon Box
patreon.description: This box is only for our loyal patrons! (Unless of course they choose to trade it)

poster.name: Motivational Poster
poster.description: Provides a 5% work payout bonus, stacking up to 50%. Found from the manager job.

ectoplasm.name: Ectoplasm
ectoplasm.description: Some gross ghost left their gunk everywhere, sell it! Found from the ghost job.

diaper.name: Used Diaper
diaper.description: Throw this used diaper at someone to prevent them from joining or starting a heist for 12 hours. Found from the housewife job.

likebutton.name: Like Button
likebutton.description: Like any other YouTuber, you should beg and collect these likes as much as you can. They are IMPORTANT TO BEING A GREAT YOUTUBER!!

taco.name: Crunchy Taco
taco.description: Eating this delicious taco will double your level up rewards for 24 hours. Found from the fast food worker job.

tipjar.name: Tip Jar
tipjar.description: You can check this tip jar once every hour! Sometimes you can find some neat stuff... Found from the streamer job.

aplus.name: A plus
aplus.description: An A+ you can sell for some profit, woo for cheating! Found from the teacher job.

policebadge.name: Police Badge
policebadge.description: A shiny police badge, found in the police station on the ground. Found from the police job.

binary.name: Binary
binary.description: A rouge piece of binary code spit out of a computer. Found from the developer job.

cash.name: Stack of Cash
cash.description: A tradeable item with the bot. Use it to trade for banknotes or pizzas. Found from the politician job.

beaker.name: Beaker of sus fluid
beaker.description: Dear god do NOT drink this. Found from the scientist job.

santasbag.name: Santa's Bag
santasbag.description: Santa has a bag full of goodies. Some pretty rare goodies too. Found from the Santa job.

ammo.name: Ammo
ammo.description: While this item is active (1 hour), you will always find an animal while hunting. Found from the Hunter job.

bait.name: Fishing Bait
bait.description: While this item is active (1 hour), you will always find something while fishing. Found from the Fisherman job.

collar.name: Pet Collar
collar.description: Owning this item gives you double xp for pets! Found from the vet job.

banhammer.name: Ban Hammer

vaccine.name: Vaccine

stonkmachine.description: Use this machine to try and earn some coins from stonk investment. Warning, there is a 10% chance to lose 10% of your wallet from a bad investment! Found from the day trader job.

memepills.name: Meme pills
memepills.description: Pills that have literally no function besides selling. Found from the pharmacist job.

energydrink.name: Energy Drink
energydrink.description: A delicious energy drink. Found from the pro gamer job.

whiskey.name: Bottle of Whiskey
whiskey.description: A superior alcohol, gives you a better chance to steal from someone and has no negative effects (lasts 15 hours). Found from the bartender job.

robbersmask.name: Robbers Mask
robbersmask.description: Your name will not show up on steal or bankrob notifs sent to the victim for 12 hours after using. Found from the robber job.

baby.name: Baby
baby.description: We do NOT sell babies guys. We simply collect them. IN THE GAME, THIS IS A JOKE WTF. Found from the babysitter job.

lawdegree.name: Law Degree

coupon.name: Shop Coupon
coupon.description: You will have the option to use this at a shop checkout. You can get 5% off any purchase from the shop. Found from the shopkeeper job.
